to the prosperity of the nation.

14
00:00:58,020 --> 00:00:59,620
He often said,

15
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:02,340
all our research

16
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:05,540
has the potential to change the world.

17
00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:09,700
I do not fear his passing,

18
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:13,700
