146
00:14:35,220 --> 00:14:40,580
♪You turn and look back at me♪

147
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:47,220
♪In those same eyes
familiar tears quietly appear♪

148
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:53,700
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

149
00:14:54,980 --> 00:15:00,460
♪So many questions time itself
