150
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:06,900
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

151
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:13,860
♪Every dream I had became
something I want with you near♪

152
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:21,220
♪How many letters
have I written just for you♪

153
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:27,020
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

154
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:34,059
♪From this life on no distance
could keep us apart♪

155
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:36,939
♪The promise we made♪

156
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:40,619
♪Will find its way
to be fulfilled one day♪

157
00:15:40,620 --> 00:15:47,219
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

158
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:53,620
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

159
00:15:54,020 --> 00:16:00,339
♪Can we still rewrite
the ending we face♪

160
00:16:00,340 --> 00:16:05,460
